        "action": "Extend Driving/Motorcycle theory certificates",
        "additional_details": "Can the government work with the DVSA to extend certificates of those who have passed and are unable to still take their Driving/motorcycle test.",
        "background": "During the start of the global pandemic as of March 2020, thousands of people have passed their driving/riding theory test. Due to the pandemic many tests are constantly cancelled due to lockdown and the certificates only last 2 years.",
